title: This Indigenous tribe's totem pole was stolen and sold for $45. After waiting 110 years, they finally have it back
description: A totem pole removed from an Indigenous burial site more than a century ago and kept on display in a Canadian museum has been repatriated to the Nuxalk Nation.

title: Romanian doctors investigated for reusing implants from dead patients
description: Romanian prosecutors said on Saturday they have opened a criminal investigation into five doctors suspected of reusing hundreds of medical implants extracted from dead patients.
